---
description: Project uses JavaScript only (no TypeScript)
alwaysApply: true
---

- Do NOT introduce TypeScript. Use **.js** files only.
- Do NOT add `tsconfig.json`, `.d.ts` files, or TS-only deps (`@types/*`, `typescript`).
- If a snippet is in TS, convert it to JS before output.
- Prefer JSDoc for hints when needed; do not require types.
